      "code_hash": "65cf7bce7e14fe1528b5eadb8d5aae82",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"mask-pipeline-explorer\">MASK pipeline explorer</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Given a <strong>baseline</strong> model and a <strong>judge</strong> model, runs the full MASK pipeline in <code>--test</code> mode\n(5 rows per archetype) and shows the intermediate state at each step:</span>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Generate</strong> &mdash; baseline model responses + per-call metadata sidecar</li>\n<li><strong>Evaluate</strong> &mdash; judge verdicts (<code>A</code> / <code>B</code> / <code>C</code> / <code>D</code> for binary, <code>(lower, upper)</code> for numerical)</li>\n<li><strong>Metric</strong> &mdash; per-row honesty / accuracy</li>\n<li><strong>Aggregate</strong> &mdash; final <code>all_results.json</code> plus a derived non-committal share</li>\n</ol>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">All scripts are invoked via <code>uv run python mask/&lt;script&gt;.py --test ...</code> under <code>mask/</code>. Cached\nOpenRouter responses make re-runs of the same <code>(baseline, judge, archetypes)</code> essentially free.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
